{"type": "article", "id": 15171, "title": "竹筒镜子", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-21T07:39:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115214M362gOwqGpls85Bx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t台湾设计师范承宗设计了一款镜子“circle”，在今年的巴黎家装博览会上展出。这款镜子有一个竹筒底座，与圆面镜子之间留出了一个空间，让镜子顿时显得轻盈而优雅，也可以放置小的饰品。立体的小圆筒与平面的大镜子构成有趣的对比，都是圆的不同体现。而花瓣形的开口和背面的竹子纹理也使镜子保留了古色古香的韵味。<a href=\"http://www.chengtsung.com/Circle\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142436aE8lWbd7ifSK1rLT.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142437A5btN3pZnTHyfU6V.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142437nwVjohWsTML1uS2r.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424386V5PB0wMve1WXlaN.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"617\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75427873\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}